ğŸ” Face-Lock Folder Access
A security-focused desktop application that restricts access to folders using facial recognition. The app ensures only the authorized user can open the folder â€” any unauthorized attempt triggers an automatic folder closure.

ğŸ§  How It Works
Folder is opened â†’ Triggers the app.

Camera activates â†’ Captures the current user's face.

Face vector comparison:

Converts the stored authorized user's face into black and white.

Uses face recognition algorithm to extract facial features.

Converts features into a vector.

Repeats the same process with the newly captured face.

Cosine Similarity Check:

Compares both face vectors.

If similarity is above threshold, folder stays open.

If below, the folder closes immediately.

